### Admin API

# Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admins/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=admin@example.com&password=admin123

### Create Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Get All Admins
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admins

### Get Admin by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admins/1

### Update Admin
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admins/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "newpassword123"
}

### Delete Admin
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admins/1

