### Medicament API

### Create Medicament
POST http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Paracetamol",
  "prixAchat": 5.0,
  "prixVente": 10.0,
  "quantiteStock": 100,
  "seuilAlerte": 20,
  "dateExpiration": "2024-12-31",
  "fournisseur": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

### Get All Medicaments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments

### Get Medicament by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments/1

### Update Medicament
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Paracetamol",
  "prixAchat": 5.0,
  "prixVente": 12.0,
  "quantiteStock": 100,
  "seuilAlerte": 20,
  "dateExpiration": "2024-12-31",
  "fournisseur": {
    "id": 1
  }
}

### Delete Medicament
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments/1

### Search Medicaments by Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments/search?nom=Para

### Get Medicaments by Fournisseur
GET http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments/fournisseur/1

### Update Stock
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/medicaments/1/stock?quantite=10

### Achat API

### Create Achat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/achats
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dateAchat": "2023-06-15",
  "fournisseur": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "ligneAchats": [
    {
      "medicament": {
        "id": 1
      },
      "quantite": 50,
      "prixUnitaire": 5.0,
      "dateExpiration": "2024-12-31"
    },
    {
      "medicament": {
        "id": 2
      },
      "quantite": 30,
      "prixUnitaire": 8.0,
      "dateExpiration": "2024-10-15"
    }
  ]
}

### Get All Achats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/achats

### Get Achat by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/achats/1

### Delete Achat
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/achats/1

### Get Achats by Date Range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/achats/date?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-12-31

### Get Achats by Fournisseur
GET http://localhost:8080/api/achats/fournisseur/1

### Get Achats by Date Range and Fournisseur
GET http://localhost:8080/api/achats/search?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-12-31&fournisseurId=1

### Get Lignes Achat by Achat
GET http://localhost:8080/api/achats/1/lignes

